### Position endpoints — Makima API
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

@base_url = http://localhost:3000
# Replace with the JWT returned from register or login.
@access_token = <access_token>
@portfolio_id = <portfolio_id>

### List open positions in a portfolio
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/portfolios/{{portfolio_id}}/positions
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### List positions including closed ones
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/portfolios/{{portfolio_id}}/positions?show_closed=true
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
